                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120701-62-off347 t18120701-62-cd348"></join>, twenty pounds weight of soap, value 15 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120701-62-victim562" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Slaymaker
                  <interp inst="t18120701-62-victim562" type="surname" value="Slaymaker"></interp>
