                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120701-62-victim562 t18120701-62-viclabel349"></join>. I live in <placeName id="t18120701-62-crimeloc350">Redcross-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18120701-62-crimeloc350" type="placeName" value="Redcross-street"></interp>
