                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120701-62-off347 t18120701-62-crimeloc350"></join>. I have no doubt that these pieces were of the same boil that I was drawing out.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I know nothing about the soap.</p>
